Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-hydro-genpy, ros-hydro-rosgraph, ros-hydro-roslib, ros-hydro-rosmsg, ros-hydro-rospy
Description: rosservice contains the rosservice command-line tool for listing and querying ROS Services. It also contains a Python library for retrieving information about Services and dynamically invoking them. The Python library is experimental and is for internal-use only.
